output.name: GlassLensWatch
output.description: GlassLensWatch is an independent, nonprofit newsroom dedicated to producing investigative journalism in the public interest. With a team of over 100 dedicated journalists, the organization focuses on uncovering impactful stories that hold power to account and drive real-world change. By blending rigorous data analysis with compelling narrative, GlassLensWatch champions transparency, inclusivity, and accountability in media, all while fostering a diverse and innovative newsroom environment.
